           for purposes not explicitly covered in this License

  2.5  PRIVATE DATA & DATASET SOVEREIGNTY
       ────────────────────────────────────
       The dataset referenced by, included within, or generated for
       this project is CLASSIFIED PRIVATE DATA. The following are
       STRICTLY PROHIBITED without written authorization:

